{"tid":2166401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨如何顛覆美國(及主要民主國家)","createTime":"2020-08-20T11:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T12:08:08.000Z","uid":24345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46681e71be379e3b3f0703e119ed40b82b6fb750","tid":2166401,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"咁啱有段新片剪得好正，想大家重溫下高學歷廢青巴個高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cJZwRUQiinA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcJZwRUQiinA&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5UwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=d9d55313\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cJZwRUQiinA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【爆po再開】遊行冇用，勇武冇用，黃經濟圈冇用，罷工冇用，黎明冇用，民意逆轉，開始攰，送頭，中計，係鬼，前線死嗮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778543\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778543</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。由意志崩壞（demoralisation）開始，令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕裂，以致崩潰，不戰而敗。呢套理論有學名，叫「顛覆」Subversion，而達到顛覆嘅行爲，就叫做 active measures / активные мероприятия。"},{"pid":"55409862143de98d53e12f3b5747683e18375502","tid":2166401,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6788b23026e86ac3422770401edb73047915b0a5","tid":2166401,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b75026e0bb1bf6da4e8b0fab9afa24944876a8","tid":2166401,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}